import ProseLayout from '../layouts/ProseLayout.astro';
---

<ProseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How GLANCE Apps handles your data. Short version: we don't collect it."
  lastUpdated="May 23, 2026"
>
  <p class="lead">
    Short version: GLANCE Apps does not collect, store, or share your personal
    data. Your information stays on your device.
  </p>

  <h2>Who we are</h2>
  <p>
    GLANCE Apps is an independent software studio publishing applications
    including dayGLANCE, lifeGLANCE, and lastGLANCE. This privacy policy covers
    our publisher-level practices and the glance-apps.com website. Each app may
    have additional privacy details specific to its features; see the privacy
    policy linked from each app's product page.
  </p>

  <h2>Data stored on your device</h2>
  <p>
    All content you create within our Apps is stored locally on your device
    using your platform's standard on-device storage. This data remains under
    your control at all times.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you use your platform's automatic backup service (iCloud Backup, Google
    Backup, or similar), your device data may be backed up as part of your
    standard device backup. This is governed by your platform provider's privacy
    policy.
  </p>

  <h2>Optional cloud sync</h2>
  <p>
    Some Apps offer optional cloud sync either to a destination you control
    (such as WebDAV, Nextcloud, or iCloud Drive) or to GLANCEvault, our
    self-hostable sync server. When using a hosted GLANCEvault instance
    operated by GLANCE Apps, your data is encrypted end-to-end before leaving
    your device and we cannot access its contents. Sync is off by default.
  </p>

  <h2>Data we do not collect</h2>
  <p>
    Our Apps are designed to operate entirely on your device. We do not:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Require you to create an account</li>
    <li>Collect personally identifiable information</li>
    <li>Transmit your notes, entries, or any app content to any servers we control</li>
    <li>Track your location</li>
    <li>Use advertising identifiers</li>
    <li>Sell or share your data with third parties</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>
    We do not use third-party analytics services. Your platform's distribution
    service (such as Apple's App Store Connect or Google Play Console) may share
    aggregated, anonymized crash and usage data with us if you have opted into
    analytics on your device. This data cannot be used to identify you individually.
  </p>

  <h2>This website</h2>
  <p>
    The glance-apps.com website is a static site served via Vercel. Vercel may
    collect standard web server logs (IP address, request times, page URLs) for
    operational purposes. We do not use cookies, tracking pixels, or analytics
    scripts on this site.
  </p>

  <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
  <p>
    Our Apps are not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect
    information from children.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>
    If we make material changes to this policy, we will update the "Last updated"
    date at the top of this page and notify users through the Apps or this website
    before changes take effect.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about our privacy practices? We're happy to answer them.
  </p>
  <p>
    <a href="mailto:privacy@glance-apps.com">privacy@glance-apps.com</a>
  </p>
</ProseLayout>
